name: A Mercurial Toast to Poe
description: Another delightful vintage mintage- repurposing the only record left of a still-life drawing I rendered in art class, 1991; now newly celebrated as an NFT, and infused with a crater found on Mercury, acquired from the MESSENGER Mission, July 03, 2011 || See NASA JPL Photojournal PIA16755, "A Toast to Dear Old Poe" ||
